述</th>\n<th>下载地址</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>DevToys</td>\n<td>本地格式转化</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/ObuchiYuki/DevToysMac\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Syntax Highlight</td>\n<td>文件预览高亮代码</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/sbarex/SourceCodeSyntaxHighlight/\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>surge</td>\n<td>多端配置同步，代理工具</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dl.nssurge.com/mac/v4/Surge-latest.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>iTerm</td>\n<td>Mac 终端工具</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://iterm2.com/downloads.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Termius</td>\n<td>服务器管理与 ftp 传输</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://termius.com/mac-os\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Postman</td>\n<td>API 管理工具</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.postman.com/downloads/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sublime Text</td>\n<td>文本编辑与查看</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.sublimetext.com/3\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Visual Studio Code</td>\n<td>轻量级代码编辑</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/download\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>IntelliJ IDEA</td>\n<td>Java 开发必备</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/idea/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DataGrip</td>\n<td>数据库管理，pg</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/datagrip/download/#section=mac\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DBeaver</td>\n<td>开源数据库工具</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dbeaver.io/download/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table><h4>目前还没有找到的软件</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>文件预览软件，不只是代码，还希望可以预览 pdf 、图片、md 等文件</li>\n<li>图片查看软件有推荐吗，希望可以使用滚轮进行缩放与放大</li>\n<li>PDF 查看软件</li>\n<li>支持 m1 的虚拟机，最好是免费的，pd 太贵了，占用内存也很大</li>\n</ol>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894110","replies":65,"created_ts":1668056496,"created":"13:01:36","title":"Mac 使用软件分享，抛砖引玉","author":"Aurora0","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Aurora0","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/grav